comments.content: NetPath 18 - IL-6 signaling pathway. [NetPath](http://www.netpath.org) is a collaborative project between [PandeyLab](http://pandeylab.igm.jhmi.edu) at Johns Hopkins University and the [Institute of Bioinformatics](http://www.ibioinformatics.org). If you use this pathway, you must cite the NetPath website until the pathway is published.
This pathway was inferred from Homo sapiens pathway [http://www.wikipathways.org/index.php?title=Pathway:WP364&oldid=28142 WP364(r28142)] with a 81% conversion rate.
